---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Delete Account — Fisch Values App"
  description="Request deletion of your Fisch Values account and all associated data."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="main">
    <div class="page-wrap">
      <h1 class="page-title">Delete Your Account</h1>

      <div class="content">
        <p>
          If you want to delete your <strong>Fisch Values</strong> account and all associated data,
          you can do it in two ways:
        </p>

        <h2>Option 1: From the App</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>Open the Fisch Values app</li>
          <li>Go to the <strong>Profile</strong> tab</li>
          <li>Tap <strong>Settings</strong></li>
          <li>Tap <strong>Delete Account</strong></li>
          <li>Confirm the deletion</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Option 2: By Email</h2>
        <p>
          Send an email to <a href="mailto:andresfelipeguzmanaleans@gmail.com">andresfelipeguzmanaleans@gmail.com</a>
          with the subject line <strong>"Delete My Account"</strong> and include the email address associated with your account.
          We will process your request within 7 business days.
        </p>

        <h2>What Data Gets Deleted</h2>
        <p>When your account is deleted, the following data is permanently removed:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your profile information (display name, email, avatar)</li>
          <li>Your trade listings and offers</li>
          <li>Your chat messages and direct messages</li>
          <li>Your reviews</li>
          <li>Your inventory and wishlist</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          All personal data is deleted within 30 days of your request. Anonymized, aggregated data
          (such as total trade counts) may be retained as it cannot be linked back to your account.
        </p>

        <p><strong>This action is permanent and cannot be undone.</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .main {
    padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .page-wrap {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .content ul, .content ol {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .content strong {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .content a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .content a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
</style>
